* **STAR Method Mapping:** Translated pure backend engineering feats (e.g., reducing A* route recalculation latency by 12ms at HackBMU) into structured behavioral talking points ready for technical interviews.
* **Elevator Pitch Compilation:** A 30-second professional introduction algorithmically optimized to highlight execution under pressure and systems programming depth.

